item.title: 8 Tips To Write Clean Code
item.description: Clean code is code that's easy to read, maintain, and understand. I consider writing clean code a skill. And it's a skill that you can learn and improve with deliberate practice. My favorite approach to practice clean coding is doing refactoring exercises. So I prepared one for you today, and we're going to improve one step at a time by applying clean code principles.
